<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 1998-07-16 01:26 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A7501 &Cx1f; tab-z
r k &Cx13;  &Cx11;  BC-CX-HIGH-RISE-DEMISE-7     07-16 1601
</HEADER>
<BODY>
<SLUG> BC-CX-HIGH-RISE-DEMISE-750&AMP;add-ECONOMIST-NYTSF </SLUG>
<HEADLINE>
GOOD RIDDANCE: WRECKING BALL TOPPLES CHICAGO PUBLIC HOUSING  
 
</HEADLINE>
  
 (ATTN: Chicago...NOTE 525-WORD TRIM; UNCUT RUNS 1,300)   (This excellent ``separate buy'' article is from the current (week
beginning 11 July 1998) Economist magazine.)  
  
 (EDITORS: We regret that this material is NOT available to clients
in Canada except to The Toronto Globe &AMP; Mail.)  
  
