homely, no-frills Beetle, is moving upscale. By Edmund L. Andrews.
</P>
<P>
   MICROSOFT-EARNINGS (Undated) _ Microsoft will post earnings and
is expected to come in at 48 cents a share. By John Markoff.
</P>
