business groups and his own Republican leadership, Rep. Lamar
Smith, R-Texas, continues to insist that any new visas for foreign
workers be tied to more protections for U.S. workers. At a news
conference Thursday, Smith presents a tech worker from Williamson
County and two other Texans who he says are jobless or
underemployed because of foreign workers. (Harlan, Cox News Service
500).
