<BODY>
<SLUG> BC-SOLAR17-COX </SLUG>
<HEADLINE>
&HT;   
</HEADLINE>
 &HT;    SOLAR POWER USE GROWING AS COST DROPS, REPORT SAYS
 &HT;    460&AMP;add
 &HT;    Moving in (w) Washington and (f) financial categories.
 &HT;    By SAMAR ABULHASSAN
