<DATE_TIME> 1998-07-16 17:40 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A8694 &Cx1f; taf-z
u e &Cx13;  &Cx11;  BC-FORTUNE-BOOK-REVIEW-N     07-16 1020
