</P>
<P>
   NAACP-AWARDS_ ATLANTA _ A look at who got the big NAACP awards:
the Thalheimer awards for chapters and the Spingarn Award (to
Myrlie Evers Williams presented by Coretta Scott King). (Oglesby,
Atlanta Journal-Constitution). 8-10.
