<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 1998-07-16 19:00 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A8881 &Cx1f; taf-z
u e &Cx13;  &Cx11;  BC-VIDEO-ART-620&AMP;ADD-NYT     07-16 0659
