and Carol Fornoff _ kick off Arizona Republican Rep. Matt Salmon's
new bill, Aimee's Law. The bill is designed to force states to
imprison violent criminals longer or make them forfeit federal
funding to another state where that criminal commits the next
crime. But critics say the bill is likely unconstitutional
electioneering. By ADRIANNE FLYNN. Story will move in the ``A''
