literally run in and run out after checking out books. That's
because of the mounds of pigeon droppings in the air ducts and on
the roof of the building - no isolated incident in Mohave County.
Earlier this week, the county the supervisors passed a measure
fining anyone $100 for feeding pigeons in the county. By MARK
SHAFFER. Stor will move in the ``A'' category. &QL; 
 &QL; 
