for the End of the Century,'' an installation piece which is the
best work this artist - one of the top three in Arizona - has done
in a decade. Story is a review and retrospective of Scholder's
career. By RICHARD NILSEN. With SCHOLDER-SIDE and PHOTOS. Story
already moved in the ``E'' category.  &QL; 
