lucrative slot machines on its reservation near upscale Scottsdale.
But Gov. Jane Hull had made no decision Thursday to sign an
agreement, saying instead she will meet with tribal officials to
discuss the high court's ruling. By VICTORIA HARKER and CAROL
SOWERS. Story will move in the ``A'' category. &QL; 
 &QL;
